# Failure-lesson directory

Lessons in this directory are produced by the evolve-retrospective subagent
when a cycle's audit returns FAIL or WARN. Each .yaml file describes one
root cause of the failure plus a preventiveAction for future cycles.

Schema: see agents/evolve-retrospective.md § 'Write the lesson YAML(s)'.
Lifecycle: see skills/evolve-loop/phase6-learn.md.
